text: Koshelevka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Vatazhensky Selsoviet, Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 118 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km east from Krasny Yar. == References == Category:Rural localities in Krasnoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Koshelevka
